Package: sglr
Type: Package
Title: Sequential Generalized Likelihood Ratio boundaries for pre-licensure vaccine trials
Version: 0.07
Date: 2010-04-20
Author: Balasubramanian Narasimhan (with input from Tze Lai and Mei-Chiung Shih)
Maintainer: Balasubramanian Narasimhan <naras@stanford.edu>
Description: Functions for computing the boundaries for pre-licensure vaccine trials using the Generalized Likelihood Ratio tests proposed by Shih, Lai, Heyse and Chen
Depends: R (>= 2.7), ggplot2, Cairo, shiny
License: GPL (>= 2)
